title: #169 - Shane Mauss & ME
description: Comedian Shane Mauss & I hang out in the Mancave and talk about getting complaints at Comedy Clubs, his LA Ayahuasca experience, DMT, his broken heels, and doing cocaine with the Mexican cartel in Texas.
